OL,3,CGovernment considers measures to
OL,4,Cprotect most disabled ahead of benefit
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FDowning Street is considering whether
OL,8,Fto introduce a measure to protect the
OL,9,Fmost disabled when they cut benefits
OL,10,Ffor those who are judged to be out of
OL,11,Fwork.
OL,13,FI understand that conversations are
OL,14,Ftaking place as officials brace
OL,15,Fthemselves for a potential rebellion
OL,16,Fover welfare cuts that will be laid
OL,17,Fout next week, including big
OL,18,Freductions to the rate of sickness
OL,19,Fbenefits.
