OL,3,CGovernment considers measures to
OL,4,Cprotect most disabled ahead of benefit
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe plans - revealed exclusively by
OL,8,FITV News last week - will see the
OL,9,Fbasic rate of Universal Credit (UC)
OL,10,Fraised to try to incentivise people to
OL,11,Fstay in the work-search group.
OL,13,FBut the highest level of UC - for the
OL,14,Fmost disabled or ill who have been
OL,15,Fjudged unable to work - will go down.
OL,17,FAt the moment you get more than #400
OL,18,Fextra if you are judged too ill to
OL,19,Fwork; that gap will be reduced.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
