OL,4,Cprotect most disabled ahead of benefit
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FThe measures are due to be "scored" on
OL,8,FRachel Reeves spring budget.
OL,10,FBut sources have told me that they are
OL,11,Flikely to also consult on measures to
OL,12,Fprotect at least a small group who are
OL,13,Fconsidered to be the most disabled.
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
