OL,3,CGovernment considers measures to
OL,4,Cprotect most disabled ahead of benefit
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FAnd the government also plans to save
OL,8,F#5bn by hitting a benefit that has
OL,9,Fnothing to do with work - Personal
OL,10,FIndependence Payments - raising the
OL,11,Fthreshold to take out those who have
OL,12,Flower-level disabilities.
OL,14,FThe move on PIP - which is meant to
OL,15,Fcover the additional costs of
OL,16,Fdisability - is expected to hit a
OL,17,Fnumber of people with mental health
OL,18,Fproblems.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
