OL,3,CGovernment considers measures to
OL,4,Cprotect most disabled ahead of benefit
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FWhen I revealed these plans last week,
OL,8,FI asked how the government would
OL,9,Fprotect the most disabled on UC - who
OL,10,Fwould be among those losing money and
OL,11,Fwas told there wasn't a mitigation,
OL,12,Fbut it's my understanding they are
OL,13,Fworking on that now. However, it will
OL,14,Fonly be consulted upon.
OL,16,FSome Labour MPs reacted furiously to
OL,17,Fthe leak - with many on the left
OL,18,Ftaking to social media to set out
OL,19,Ftheir anger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
