OL,3,CGovernment considers measures to
OL,4,Cprotect most disabled ahead of benefit
OL,5,Ccuts
OL,7,FBut even moderate MPs have privately
OL,8,Ftold me they have major concerns.
OL,10,FOne told colleagues in a WhatsApp
OL,11,Fgroup that while they agreed to the
OL,12,Fprinciples of getting people into
OL,13,Fwork, they were worried about the
OL,14,Fmessaging.
OL,16,F"We have to get this right. We have
OL,17,Fgone from being well thought of last
OL,18,Fweek following Starmer's leadership
OL,19,Fback to the party to appearing to
OL,20,Fattack disabled people when that is
OL,21,Fnot the intent."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
