OL,7,FAnother said they were "extremely
OL,8,Fconcerned" with inboxes inundated with
OL,9,Fworried constituents but also claimed
OL,10,FMPs were "terrified of speaking out".
OL,12,FSome are talking about a rebellion of
OL,13,Fbetween 40 and 100 MPs as some of the
OL,14,FPIP changes - which include freezing
OL,15,Fthe benefit next year - will require
OL,16,Flegislation.
